<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='6960' id='t-6960'>Now...</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='9200' id='t-9200'>let's go back in time.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='12560' id='t-12560'>It's 1974.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='17960' id='t-17960'>There is the gallery somewhere</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='21880' id='t-21880'>in the world,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='25080' id='t-25080'>and there is a young girl, age 23,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='28400' id='t-28400'>standing in the middle of the space.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='32759' id='t-32759'>In the front of her is a table.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='37000' id='t-37000'>On the table there are 76 objects</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='42720' id='t-42720'>for pleasure and for pain.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='46520' id='t-46520'>Some of the objects are</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='48720' id='t-48720'>a glass of water, a coat, a shoe, a rose.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='55160' id='t-55160'>But also the knife,
the razor blade, the hammer</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='61800' id='t-61800'>and the pistol with one bullet.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='66240' id='t-66240'>There are instructions which say,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='69240' id='t-69240'>&quot;I'm an object.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='71000' id='t-71000'>You can use everything on the table on me.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='74360' id='t-74360'>I'm taking all responsibility --
even killing me.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='78920' id='t-78920'>And the time is six hours.&quot;</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 1:34
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='83600' id='t-83600'>The beginning of this
