<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='91880' id='t-91880'>they'd give me the rose.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='94120' id='t-94120'>But very soon after,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='96920' id='t-96920'>there was a man who took the scissors
