<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='138920' id='t-138920'>And after six hours were finished,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='141680' id='t-141680'>I...</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='144200' id='t-144200'>started walking towards the public.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='147360' id='t-147360'>I was a mess.</span>
