<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='162760' id='t-162760'>And then --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='165080' id='t-165080'>what happened</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='167240' id='t-167240'>is I went to the hotel,
