<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='327320' id='t-327320'>Our relationship was 12 years,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='329560' id='t-329560'>and we worked on so many subjects,
both male and female energy.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='333440' id='t-333440'>And as every relationship
comes to an end, ours went too.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='337600' id='t-337600'>We didn't make phone calls
